form models. Hence, we stress the necessity of accurate waveform\nmodels that include physical effects such as higher-order modes to trust future\ntests of General Relativity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Feb 2018 15:33:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-07"}
